data.description: * Amazing Opportunity to own a Newer Beautiful Home built in 2008.       * 2678 sqft -   7,293  lot.       * 4 bedrooms  + 3 Bath + LARGE great room.       * en-suite bathroom, separate shower, soaking tub, dual sinks,  LARGE Custom-made walk-in closet.        * Large  covered patio.       * Three-car garage.        * Insulated storage room.        * Just minutes from Quai Elementary, Shadow Hills Magnet School, Kaiser, Walmart,  Lowes, Community park and multiple restaurants.   !!Join us at one of our Open Houses or contact us today for a private viewing!!
